{
  "description": {
    "description of test case": "Decomposed four-chamber closed-loop heart model. Uses ChamberElastanceInductor, ValveTanh, BloodVessel, and BloodVesselRC. Parameters from Sankaran et al. 2012 and Menon et al. 2023.",
    "circuit": "RA -> TV -> RV -> PV -> pul_vessel -> LA -> MV -> LV -> AV -> aortic_cap -> branch0_seg0 -> sys_Rp -> sys_Rd -> RA"
